# 📊 Business Sales Performance Analytics

## 🔍 Project Overview
This project analyzes business sales data to uncover key insights related to revenue trends, product performance, and regional sales distribution.
The objective is to simulate a real-world business scenario where data-driven decisions help improve performance and growt

## 📁 Dataset
The dataset contains:
* Order Date
* Sales
* Profit
* Category
* Region
* Product Name
  
## 🛠 Tools Used
* Tableau (for data visualization & dashboard)
* Excel (for data cleaning and preprocessing)

## 📊 Key Analysis Performed
* Revenue trends over time
* Top-selling products
* Category-wise performance
* Region-wise sales analysis

## 🧠 Key Insights

* Sales show seasonal variation with a peak in November
* Technology category generates the highest revenue
* West region is the top-performing region
* A few products contribute significantly to total sales

---

## 💡 Business Recommendations

* Focus on high-performing products to maximize revenue
* Improve marketing strategies in low-performing regions
* Leverage seasonal demand with targeted campaigns
* Optimize pricing for better profitability

